{"tid":1286413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真正挑動中共神經既做法","createTime":"2019-07-05T00:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:14:37.000Z","uid":34415,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e23755d5a914d372f348bdb363cf16abb2ca62cb","tid":1286413,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T00:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRJkX7W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRJkX7W.png&h=c12a77f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BysmHzz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBysmHzz.png&h=a871f28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港-東突厥友誼永固】<br />\n<br />\n東突厥斯坦人民所受到的可怕壓逼，是香港人全體奮起反送中的源動力。皆因我們都知道，送中條例一過，我們所知道的集中營非人待遇、因全家被抓而凍死河邊的維吾爾孤兒、被施打藥物化學絕育的維吾爾女性、僅因裝修風格堅持維吾爾文化就被拉人封舖的可怕下場，將發生在每一個香港人身上。<br />\n<br />\n半年前我們舉出中國各地的獨派旗幟，共同聲討共產中國的反人類暴行，結果倉庫被破壞，旗幟被偷走而至今尚未破案(想想也是理所當然的)。半年後在立法會看見這一幕，我們心感欣慰，一切努力都沒有白費。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族將繼續與東突厥斯坦人民同行，沒有東西可以打斷兩族之間在同一戰線上鑄就的情誼！香港獨立！東突厥斯坦獨立！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1910932979167811/posts/2332716930322745/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1910932979167811%2Fposts%2F2332716930322745%2F&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=5eb697b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1910932979167811/posts/2332716930322745/</a><br />\n======================================<br />\n為免再受奶共FB封禁，請盡速Follow本組織以下平台的專頁<br />\nInstagram：<br />\nhk_national_front<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hk_national_front/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhk_national_front%2F&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=8114a1b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hk_national_front/</a><br />\nTwitter：<br />\n香港民族陣綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKNationalFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https